snippet.title: Codename:Terranova - Launch Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Codename: Terranova is out now! Buy the game on Steam:
https://bit.ly/300etST

Codename Terranova is a co-op communication game that put the players the Agent / Operator roles
Take your partner to a game in which every second counts and beat all the other teams among the globe and beyond!
Your team will have to show that they are a perfect match to overcome any adversity. 
Everyone is invited to try, but few are destined to succeed.

Will you be among them?

Play with Codename: Terranova and help us shape up the game!

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ACGamesTeam/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ACGamesTeam
Discord: https://discord.gg/Bth4MFf
